Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Kavana M ",
    "email": "kavana@example.com",
    "password": "123456"
       
}
### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "kavana@example.com",
    "password": "123456"
}
### Add Menu Item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menu
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "restaurant_id": 1,
    "name": "Paneer Pizza",
    "price": 299,
    "is_available": true
}

### Get All Menu Items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menu

### Update Menu Item
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/menu/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "restaurant_id": 1,
    "name": "Veg Supreme Pizza",
    "price": 349,
    "is_available": true
}
### Delete Menu Item
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/menu/1

